text: do you like children?
I like children individually, groups of children not so much.
are you worried about poor children?
Yes, I think taking care of children is important
are you worried about children not getting enough to eat?
Of course, everyone has the right to food.
how about education, are you worried about children growing up ignorant?
Yes, education is extremely important
do you think children should have a roof over their heads?
Yes, I think any decent person would
how much does it take to feed a child without a family in the third world per day?
I really have no idea. Maybe 5 dollars?
can you believe it is less than that?
Ya i guess I could believe that
are you interested in helping a poor childe with a contribution?
Yes I am
have you heard about save the children fund?
No, tell me about it
it is a program to help poor children around the world with basic needs. do you want to help them?
Yes I do
look them up in the web and make a dontation please! ..thanks in advance!
Ok, I will
